summary:
I Start playing tennis when I was 5 years old.
Have always been by the best of 3 in the tennis rankings in Holland so I have been traveling a lot around Europe and South America for playing tournaments. 
When I was 15 years old I became a proffesional tennis player and played Roland Garros, Wimbledon and US Open.
Unfortunately due to an injury on my hip when I was 18 years old the dutch tennis association (KNLTB) stopt sponsering me financially and I had to stop playing professional, so I attended the sport school ( Cios) for 2 years. 
After I attended the sport school I went to America to play college tennis for the University of Mississippi(Ole Miss) having a full scholarship. I graduated when I was 25 years old with cum laude in Parks and Recreation Management. 
Nowadays I am teaching tennis lessons to various levels in Belgium.
People also can email me at somersilona@hotmail.com
